01:06:34.536 --> 01:06:37.960
AUDIENCE: Should we avoid
potatoes, bread, rice,

01:06:37.960 --> 01:06:38.951
and pasta?

01:06:38.951 --> 01:06:40.450
MICHAEL GREGER: So
