So that's why I have this
talk about the most disabling

01:09:30.220 --> 01:09:31.160
diseases too.

01:09:31.160 --> 01:09:33.214
So, yeah, if you're
crippled with arthritis

01:09:33.214 --> 01:09:35.130
maybe you don't want to
live an extra 10 years

01:09:35.130 --> 01:09:36.420
because you can't even move.

01:09:36.420 --> 01:09:37.790
Absolutely.

