01:09:40.860 --> 01:09:44.120
that-- yeah, yeah, yeah.

01:09:44.120 --> 01:09:45.350
And so, right.

01:09:45.350 --> 01:09:47.479
So they have all
these neat metrics,

01:09:47.479 --> 01:09:48.986
like disability-adjusted
life years.

01:09:48.986 --> 01:09:50.819
So they're not just how
many years you have,

01:09:50.819 --> 01:09:52.529
but how many healthy years.

01:09:52.529 --> 01:09:54.109
And you get the
same kind of stats.

