01:14:56.890 --> 01:15:01.360
Because that's that much more
broccoli than most people eat.

01:15:01.360 --> 01:15:04.930
I mean you just can't get
kind of pounds of food

01:15:04.930 --> 01:15:06.760
in kind of the same way.

01:15:06.760 --> 01:15:09.746
And so, yeah.

01:15:09.746 --> 01:15:11.620
And once you get down
to chemical components,

01:15:11.620 --> 01:15:13.494
