where it comes from.

01:15:13.494 --> 01:15:18.200
Vitamin C is ascorbic acid
however you get it from,

01:15:18.200 --> 01:15:21.210
whether you make it
synthetically in a lab.

01:15:21.210 --> 01:15:21.710
Yes?

01:15:21.710 --> 01:15:24.584
AUDIENCE: So there's practical
